{"tid":2010650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[高登舊事回顧1] 中學雞自稱黑客 挑戰高登仔","createTime":"2020-05-10T14:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T11:06:06.000Z","uid":227275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7c729a0b8e0dc5423fc40b5717db18bb8857acdb","tid":2010650,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:11:30.000Z","msg":"見到美國有15歲黑客偷左7億bitcoin 成班人都話香港人唔會出到咁既天才  令我諗起Net Send<br />\n<br />\nNet Send，一名自稱中級黑客的網民，自稱全球天才隊成員之一，識得高級HTML語法和cmd程式語言，因在facebook發表將會攻擊該網站的言論被高登人發現和起底。 其他網名: 網絡洛克人, 中級黑客<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/e2Phh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fe2Phh.png&h=c4f03956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/9/9b/JGebP.png/revision/latest?cb=20111105190307\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F9%2F9b%2FJGebP.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20111105190307&h=5846b4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在2011年10月26日，Net Send自稱將會在11月5日幫黑客群組攜手對付facebook，並宣佈該日為FaceBook之死。高登人知道Net Send的言論後對他強烈恥笑和觀看他過往言論。Net Send知道後在facebook對高登人宣戰，指高登人不可能把他起底亦自稱「我從不怕人，只有人怕我。」 高登人對Net Send極為自大的言論極為不滿，迅速將其起底。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有高登會員「我係超級比達」報警，指Net Send不誠實使用電腦，得到警方的書面回覆。<br />\n<br />\n香港討論區及Uwants因維護關閉<br />\n2011年11月5日，香港知名網站香港討論區及Uwants關閉數小時，有高登人大驚，認為Net Send與其印度黑客朋友開始進行攻擊報復，深恐Net Send有進一步行動，攻擊高登；後來有網民證實香港討論區和Uwants只是在進行系統更新及維護，因而關閉數小時。<br />\n<br />\nQOOZA-CPU電流中毒論<br />\nNet Send早在2011年1月13日發表此偉論，其後被轉載到高登，被高登人恥笑。他發現後隨即刪除此偉論。 原來插唔同既USB位,CPU電流會唔同,插後邊中毒機會低D,插前邊中毒機會高D<br />\n<br />\n黑客技術升級歷史<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/V3ktI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FV3ktI.png&h=89f2a800&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ndrop到得返電腦科<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/3/3c/369.png/revision/latest?cb=20111028165950\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F3%2F3c%2F369.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20111028165950&h=748768bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自稱有FB 妹妹 list <br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/7/7a/3692.png/revision/latest?cb=20111028165111\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F7%2F7a%2F3692.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20111028165111&h=e934eb4f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e6687c2e9fe5c058d39d3aa7e7ba6826ba66ce0","tid":2010650,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:12:29.000Z","msg":"網絡洛克人來源<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/2D1je.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2D1je.png&h=1152407c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/13/NXoXe.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20111105190435\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F13%2FNXoXe.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20111105190435&h=0fbc9500&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1880506049d21ca11dadb2daa74c67eec9132ea8","tid":2010650,"uid":52087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"呢條友都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63ffe07391a0c9b9ee4d2c1083b365909afa19cf","tid":2010650,"uid":227275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:16:09.000Z","msg":"好屌爽!<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/4BxMq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4BxMq.png&h=6a14d30e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nI laughed , really.<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jq95N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fjq95N.png&h=68383b83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知識寫C++未<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/NmniJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht